<section class="how-it-works">
  <div class="hiw-header">
    <h2 class="section-label">How It Works</h2>
    <p class="hiw-title">Three steps. MCP-first execution.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="hiw-steps">
    <div class="hiw-step">
      <div class="hiw-number">01</div>
      <div class="hiw-content">
        <h3>Install Spotter and enable hooks</h3>
        <p>One command boots Spotter, enables deterministic hook capture, and keeps your Claude workflow unchanged.</p>
        <div class="hiw-terminal">
          <span class="hiw-prompt">$</span>
          git clone https://github.com/marot/spotter && cd spotter && mix setup && mix phx.server
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-step">
      <div class="hiw-number">02</div>
      <div class="hiw-content">
        <h3>Triage in the Spotter review UI</h3>
        <p>Filter by project, hide noise, inspect transcript + terminal timelines, and prioritize with hotspots and freshness metadata.</p>
        <div class="hiw-terminal">
          <span class="hiw-prompt">$</span>
          open http://localhost:1100/reviews
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hiw-step">
      <div class="hiw-number">03</div>
      <div class="hiw-content">
        <h3>Execute fixes from Claude via MCP</h3>
        <p>Run Spotter review workflows in Claude over MCP, resolve annotations with notes, and keep an auditable trail synced back to Spotter.</p>
        <div class="hiw-terminal">
          <span class="hiw-prompt">$</span>
          claude "run spotter-review on open annotations"
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .how-it-works {
    padding: 6rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .hiw-header {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hiw-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 2.25rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0f3f8;
  }

  .hiw-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2.5rem;
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .hiw-step {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .hiw-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(212, 145, 94, 0.2);
    line-height: 1;
    padding-top: 0.15rem;
  }

  .hiw-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f0f3f8;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hiw-content p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.65;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .hiw-terminal {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
